{"tid":2203721,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新巴車長遭警控不小心駕駛11月再訊 警方保釋金高於罪行最高罰款額","createTime":"2020-09-15T13:54:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T15:02:40.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"6fe51a29e8e0a6c916dfb9c5c7e89ab3cd7f6719","tid":2203721,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T13:54:47.000Z","msg":"網民本月6日發起九龍遊行，其間警方指一名新巴970號線車長在彌敦道「無故響號」及「快速行駛」，將巴士截停，再指控車長藏有士巴拿，將他拘捕。涉案車長最終被控一項不小心駕駛罪，案件今午在九龍城裁判法院提堂，並押後至11月17日再訊，以待警方調查。控方要求被告繼續遵守警方訂下的原有保釋條件，獲裁判官張天雁批准。被告之前獲警方准以6,000元保釋，金額超過控罪最高的5,000元罰款。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200915/6QI2KME7XJBC5AU3E3QVC5KI7U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200915%2F6QI2KME7XJBC5AU3E3QVC5KI7U%2F&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIuUYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=b647fda6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200915%2F6QI2KME7XJBC5AU3E3QVC5KI7U%2F&h=9b27640c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200915/6QI2KME7XJBC5AU3E3QVC5KI7U/</a>"},{"pid":"f087ae5f28a6d7c8623a01b806cdc965fdc64eb3","tid":2203721,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T13:55:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79d023128c6120f6fc33db09f25a0d17a4ee7a42","tid":2203721,"uid":183685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T13:55:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e933eb42d375a2ca3b59196292fd2c0fe703d6f4","tid":2203721,"uid":65888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T13:55:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4dc4a582d59b